text: Tobias Heintz (born 13 July 1998) is a Norwegian footballer who plays for Sarpsborg 08, on loan from Kasımpaşa. He started his career in his local club Moss FK, before joining crosstown rivals SK Sprint-Jeløy. He made his senior debut for Sprint-Jeløy in 2014 before joining Sarpsborg 08.https://www.fotball.no/fotballdata/person/profil/?fiksId=2706562 He signed for the Turkish team Kasimpasa for 1 mil euro pluss add ons early January 2019. He made his Eliteserien debut in July 2016 against Lillestrøm SK.
